        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The Department for the Welfare of Differently Abled &amp; Senior Citizens launched the &quot;Sanctioning of Daisy Players to Visually Challenged&quot; scheme to distribute free daisy players to visually challenged students pursuing 9th Class to Degree as per the Action Plan 2017-18. The Assistant Directors and District Managers are instructed to follow these guidelines to ensure proper distribution. The application is accepted online for this scheme. \n",
        "benefits_md": "Eligible beneficiaries of this scheme will be provided with a DAISY Player to facilitate accessible learning and information access.\n<br>\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "The \"Sanctioning of Daisy Players to Visually Challenged\" scheme aims to distribute daisy players to visually challenged students pursuing 9th Class to Degree as per the Action Plan 2017-18. ",
